	<SpellDef InternalName="Droptheshoulder">
		<DisplayName>Droptheshoulder</DisplayName>
		<Description>Lower your shoulder and charge an enemy doing damage equal to your defense and knocks the target back. Severe impact causes you to miss the next turn.</Description>
		<FormattedDescription>Charge an enemy dealing (%d) damage and knockback. Miss your next turn.</FormattedDescription>
